<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - Bargain Balloons</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial, sans-serif';
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            max-width: 1200px;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 50px 0;
            background-color: #87CEEB;
            color: #fff;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 3em;
        }
        .header p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
        }
        .about-section {
            padding: 40px 0;
        }
        .about-section h2 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .about-section p {
            text-align: justify;
            line-height: 1.6;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .values-section, .team-section, .contact-section {
            padding: 40px 0;
            background-color: #fff;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .values-section h2, .team-section h2, .contact-section h2 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .values-section ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            font-size: 1.1em;
        }
        .values-section li {
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
        .team-section {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .team-member {
            margin: 10px;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            flex: 1 1 calc(33.333% - 20px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 10px;
            background-color: #f0f8ff;
        }
        .team-member img {
            border-radius: 50%;
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
        }
        .team-member h3 {
            margin: 10px 0;
            font-size: 1.5em;
        }
        .team-member p {
            font-size: 1em;
            color: #666;
        }
        .contact-section form {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .contact-section form input, .contact-section form textarea, .contact-section form button {
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 1em;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .contact-section form button {
            background-color: #87CEEB;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }
        
                flex: 1 1 100%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>About Us</h1>
        <p>Welcome to Bargain Balloons, your premier destination for high-quality balloons.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
        <section class="about-section">
            <h2>Our Story</h2>
            <p>
                Established in 2024, Bargain Balloons was born out of a passion for bringing joy and color to life's special moments. 
                Our founder,Krutik , started the company in a small workshop with a vision to create the most vibrant and durable balloons on the market. 
                Over the years, we have grown into a leading manufacturer, trusted by customers around the world for our commitment to quality and innovation.
            </p>
            <p>
                Today, we offer a diverse range of balloons in various shapes, sizes, and colors, all crafted with the highest standards of craftsmanship. 
                From festive parties to corporate events, our balloons are designed to add a touch of magic to any occasion.
            </p>
        </section>
        <section class="values-section">
            <h2>Our Values</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Quality:</strong> We pride ourselves on producing balloons that not only look great but also stand the test of time.</li>
                <li><strong>Innovation:</strong> Our team is constantly exploring new materials and designs to bring you the latest trends in balloon manufacturing.</li>
                <li><strong>Customer Satisfaction:</strong> Your happiness is our priority. We strive to provide exceptional service and products that exceed your expectations.</li>
                <li><strong>Environmental Responsibility:</strong> We are committed to sustainability and are continuously seeking ways to minimize our environmental footprint.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
        
    </div>
</body>
</html>
